Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:20.09,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I put together dried up words...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:28.83,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but all I want to do is convey\N my simple feelings to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:34.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The faint wind that blew from that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:38.40,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I threw it away in yesterday's ruins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:44.55,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So I can live today with you with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:52.19,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But still, this incident will\N continue to trouble you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:57.08,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's why it must be a goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:01:04.12,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now we just try to understand\N each other until nothing remains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:11.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And eventually, we will realize\N that it was everything to us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:18.01,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Sadness will run down our cheeks,\N creating a river of tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:28.97,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,1700)}Trembling thoughts will become a strong\N whirl and melt together into one
Comment: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:30.04,OP5,,0,0,0,,OP End
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to\Nrun away from me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo... loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:32.04,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\blur4\fad(600,600)\pos(678,542)\3c&H000000&}A Cry on Deaf Ears
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you this time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do it.\NI was not able to stop Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think...\Nthe one who can stop Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the one who can save Sasuke is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto... you are the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto... this is my...\Nonce in a lifetime... favor to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... Please bring Sasuke back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I also told this to Sakura, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Iruka Sensei, why on the earth\Ndoes an outstanding person like me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,have to be on the same team with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke graduated with\Nthe highest grade out of all students...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, you are at the bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When you even out\Nthe team's strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,then it naturally becomes like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Try your best not to slow me down,\Nyou dunce.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am fine without eating!\NI am absolutely fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked Sakura for a hint the other day,\Nwhat did she tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's with that face...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You loser...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You... I hated you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows,\Nmy body moved on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You rescue Sakura, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I could still distract him for a little while...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost everything once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see my precious comrades\Ndie in front of me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it... Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you become like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens to me,\Nwhat does that have to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter who it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody has the right\Nto tell me what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I will tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done fooling around with\Nyou guys of the Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Choji...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Go everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, quickly! I'll catch up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Neji...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiba! Akamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The strategy... a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?\NPlease go quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You also promised Sakura\Nwith a Nice-Guy pose, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bushy Brow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll defeat this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:07:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone risked their lives\Nto come after you, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Lastly, I will tell you\Nthe most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke is neither a close friend\Nof mine nor is he someone I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But Sasuke is a Shinobi of\Nthe Village Hidden in the Leaves...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.36,0:08:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we will rescue him\Nby risking our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Leaf way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you take\Nyour comrades of the Leaf?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Comrades, you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I become stronger staying\Nwith those so-called com rades?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to where Orochimaru is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru is the person who killed\Nthe Third Hokage
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and tried to crush The Leaf Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he will\Ngive you the power freely?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He just wants your body\Nas a vessel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You might not be able to come back.\NYou might get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'd easily let you\Ngo to such a place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If my goal is accomplished,\Nthen that's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you intend to get in that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it can't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna be able to!\NI'll take you back even by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you laughing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You were laughing at that time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That time...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not funny. I am happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about...\Nhow I can finally defeat you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That time you wanted to fight me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You were thrilled weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,At first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you were different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But first, put on your Headband.\NI'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just put it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to\Nput one scratch on my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:11:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that this is a sign\Nthat we fight as equal Leaf Shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what I call a stuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you and I are equal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never thought I was inferior to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so obnoxious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That was not the kind of fight I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now... this is not...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about\Nyour circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What... is this power?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Power is flowing out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the power that\Nthe guy was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, the power\Nis growing into my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is like that now...\Nif I release this curse mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how much power...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What power...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not the same as before...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I awakened long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,From my idiotic self who dreams about\Na lax peaceful future...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,hanging out with comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I left the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I sought power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream is not in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream is in the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only place it exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.16,0:17:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You hit the target right in the middle,\Neven the one behind the rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:17:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez... You said that\Nyou would teach me a new shuriken jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There is an important mission tomorrow\Nand I need to prepare for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Sasuke...\NAnother time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! If you push yourself...
